{"tid":1563432,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民陣就6.12警方投擲催淚彈的決定提出司法覆核","createTime":"2019-09-12T11:42:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T13:41:03.000Z","uid":212626,"like":44,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7915369457fec34db2586344edbbad411f546b54","tid":1563432,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:42:14.000Z","msg":"6.12反修例示威期間，民陣下午在中信大廈外舉行獲發不反對通知書的集會，警方向集會人士投擲催淚彈驅散，民陣今日就警方投擲催淚彈的決定入稟高等法院，提出司法覆核。<br />\n<br />\n民陣申請要求法庭宣布，有關決定是違法及不合憲，並要求警方遵守職責，保障集會及示威自由，透過合理適當方式，根據不反對通知書協助進行和平合法集會。<br />\n<br />\n入稟狀提到，有關決定明顯違反《香港人權法案》，亦是不必要，因為民陣集會是和平，與立法會外發生的事無關，即使立法會外的示威者走入民陣集會人士中，警方亦無緊急需要，向群眾直接發射催淚彈。<br />\n<br />\n民陣又提到，警方當時發射催淚彈，令人群陷入瘋狂，警方防線向中信大廈推進，而大廈只有一道門開放，群眾有機會嚴重受傷，認為即使警方有需要發射催淚彈，警方應該提早作出警告，並容許群眾有足夠時間散去，警方亦應提供疏散路線。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480256-20190912.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480256-20190912.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=S%2BP5iCTdX9iTDztVuYOIb%2FY%2F4yEwT0EAZMYNsJUacQ0%3D&h=4c14fd63\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1480256-20190912.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=547498d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1480256-20190912.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"9e439046f6fb6e09d77ea3a237e527493c689e96","tid":1563432,"uid":76702,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:42:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"87c3a1ffc363cf90e4dbbddd2b070a85afcb6fff","tid":1563432,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:43:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"5f76b0f8bf6cca28e330b9c4930391af489f3675","tid":1563432,"uid":1654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:44:05.000Z","msg":"好過冇"},{"pid":"f22abca05326843fc3670ea6face1d03267f8bc5","tid":1563432,"uid":36592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:44:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"12eb4de29a0acf968c8b6c60c5971d686eff19d6","tid":1563432,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:45:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ea10e92fc7e1410e64664bffd9eebc997dfe32c","tid":1563432,"uid":68111,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:47:31.000Z","msg":"睇黎係夾好今個星期黎場警權大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73bb8ce42e74b1ff7504749007f5e99a76c1fdb6","tid":1563432,"uid":126325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:47:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eaa86efc5984900cbd87e518538a9b09cfcdb0b","tid":1563432,"uid":68111,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6ea10e92fc7e1410e64664bffd9eebc997dfe32c","tid":1563432,"uid":68111,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:47:31.000Z